The MetaWare environment needs to be set up for TC4Dx:

- Type Win+r and enter command "cmd /V:ON /k C:\<MetaWare-path>\setup.bat"
- Metware version 1.1 :
 Build PPU libraries for TC4D with the command:"build -ca -sc tc4dx_system -e BUILD_CONFIG=TC4D_PPU -e BUILD_TYPE=debug"
Note : Include the mwlib library. Need to include during compilation.

- Metware version 2.0 :
 Build PPU libraries for TC4D with the command:"build -ca -sc tc4dx_system -e BUILD_CONFIG=TC4DA_PPU -e BUILD_TYPE=debug"
Note : mwlib is missing. Need to removed during compilation.
